Package: dpm-agent
Source: dpm
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Matias Bustos SM <matias.bustos@example.com>
Installed-Size: 25
Depends: python3-dpm (= 0.1.0)
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/mbustos/dpm
Description: Distributed Process Manager - agent service
 DPM agent that runs on each host in a trusted Linux cluster.
 It manages local processes (start/stop/monitor) and publishes
 telemetry and process output over LCM multicast.
 .
 Typically deployed as a systemd service (dpm-agent.service).
 .
 This package installs the systemd unit and default config.
